<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>Select the <span class="wintitle">Applications</span> tab.</li>
         <li>On the row containing the application, click <span class="menucascade">
               <span class="uicontrol">Goto application</span>
               <span class="uicontrol">SP Initiated</span>
            </span>.
         </li>
         <li>If required, sign in. The displayed results depend on the selected application type.</li>
         <li>For policy-based testing, update the URL to add an appropriate path and resend the request. The following example adds the <span class="code">/public</span> path:
            <div>
              <img src="../../Images/access-gateway/application-configure-test.policy.png"
                 id="img_new"
                 class="thumbnail"/>
             </div>
         </li>
         <li>This displays the result of applying the current user and policy. </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
</html>
